        <h2>Meet Our Founder</h2>  
        <div class="card mb-4" style="width: 18rem; margin: auto;">  
            <img src="/images/jaka.jpeg" class="card-img-top" alt="Founder Picture">  
            <div class="card-body">  
                <h5 class="card-title">Makarim Muhammad</h5>  
                <p class="card-text">Mr. Makarim is the visionary behind Parkuy, committed to revolutionizing the parking industry.</p>  
            </div>  
        </div>  
    </section>  
        <section class="mt-4">  
            <h2>Our History</h2>  
            <p>Parkuy was developed in <b>2024</b> to address the growing challenges of parking in urban areas. <b>Mr. Makarim</b>, often called <b>Mr. Jaka</b>, is the mastermind behind the application. He wanted to create a one-stop parking solution that simplifies the booking experience. Starting from humble beginnings, our company continues to grow. More than 1 million customers have used our application, and more than 1,000 parking lots have joined.</p>  
        </section>  

        <section id="our-goals" class="py-5">  
            <div class="container">  
                <h2 class="text-center mt-5">Our Goals</h2>  
                <ul class="list-unstyled">  
                    <li class="mb-5 mt-3">  
                        <h4>Simplify the Parking Process</h4>  
                        <p>We are dedicated to revolutionizing the parking process by creating intuitive and user-friendly solutions. Our aim is to minimize the complexity involved in finding and reserving parking spaces, allowing users to navigate their parking needs with ease and confidence.</p>  
                    </li>  
                    <li class="mb-5">  
                        <h4>Enhance User Experience Through Innovative Technology</h4>  
                        <p>By harnessing the power of the latest technological advancements, we strive to continually enhance the user experience. Our platform will feature intuitive interfaces, personalized preferences, and cutting-edge tools that ensure our users enjoy a seamless interaction and greater satisfaction with every visit.</p>  
                    </li>  
                    <li class="mb-0">  
                        <h4>Provide Real-Time Parking Availability Updates</h4>  
                        <p>We prioritize keeping our users informed with real-time updates on parking space availability. By integrating state-of-the-art tracking and communication systems, we empower our users to make prompt and informed decisions, ensuring they spend less time searching for parking and more time enjoying their activities.</p>  
                    </li>  
                </ul>  
            </div>  
        </section>  

        <section class="mt-1">  
            <h2>Our Vision</h2>  
            <p>Our vision is to create a smarter, more efficient parking system that simplifies the lives of drivers...</p>  
        </section>  

